        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2244062375" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1483496490807072377">Imam Ibn Katheer&apos;s رحمه الله work is always amazing and beautiful to read. However on this occasion, I have seen a lot of editing errors by Darussalam. The presentation of the content was a bit tough to go through with a lot of spelling mistakes. Please rectify this issue.</span>
  <span id="freeText1483496490807072377" style="display:none">Imam Ibn Katheer's رحمه الله work is always amazing and beautiful to read. However on this occasion, I have seen a lot of editing errors by Darussalam. The presentation of the content was a bit tough to go through with a lot of spelling mistakes. Please rectify this issue.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1483496490807072377" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
